'''Mvuu''' (''Hippopotamus'' in English) imhuka yemusango iri pamupanda we[[dzinoyamwisa]] inowanikwa mu[[Africa]] kuChamhembe kwe[[gwenga]] reSahara. Mvuu inogara chikamu chenguva mumvura chimwe chikamu padunhu. Ichitevedza [[nzou]] ne[[nhemachena]], mvuu ndiyo mhuka yechitatu pakukura kwemumhu. Mhuka iyi inofura sora nokudya miti.

